{"tid":1025121,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"跑渣馬俾人撞跌咗隻airpod，條撚樣仲要唔賠錢","createTime":"2019-02-17T06:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T09:24:34.000Z","uid":45772,"like":19,"dislike":728,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"8c301ab7948f1fe04913d6880add57f8869f1c06","tid":1025121,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"今朝跑10k 去到飲水站果到已經差唔多到頂<br />\n諗住停低飲杯水再跑 點知一伸手拎水果陣<br />\n後面條契弟一支箭衝上黎<br />\n撞到我成個人打白鴿轉<br />\n<br />\n重點係撞到我一邊airpod唔知跌左去邊<br />\n我搵左1分鐘搵唔到 即刻爆seed狂跑追條友<br />\n捉到佢之後話 跑完先處理<br />\n好啦 我等<br />\n去到終點當然就無左影<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企用佢布個號碼人肉到佢facebook<br />\n仲打哂卡 屌佢老母扮撚哂勁甘喎<br />\ninbox再問佢 佢又已讀不回<br />\n到岩岩佢覆我係咪一早跌左自己唔知咋<br />\n結果佢係話一蚊都唔賠<br />\n仲話我屈佢錢喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴絲有無計???"},{"pid":"3982cd6ed2a3ad54825a67396c6cbbf12d1437a7","tid":1025121,"uid":30186,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd48f859bb7de68a0a2071a6f5a51d10d9cb8ace","tid":1025121,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5188c38e284863469324d73bd266f6fae484474a","tid":1025121,"uid":46835,"like":5,"dislike":41,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:23:01.000Z","msg":"cap 佢個樣上嚟啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee3205a619421fbd6b51c54e8b12e9b5087987c","tid":1025121,"uid":178800,"like":442,"dislike":3,"score":439,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T06:23:16.000Z","msg":"跑渣馬仲帶airpod<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"h